Package: foundry-image-cli
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 imagemagick,
 graphicsmagick
Description: command-line image manipulation utilities
 The two canonical CLI image-processing toolkits — both useful and
 slightly different in capability and feature set:
 .
   * imagemagick      magick / convert / mogrify / identify / montage / …
   * graphicsmagick   gm (lighter fork, often faster for batch work)
